  <section aria-labelledby="ideas">
    <h2 id="ideas">Ideas in her work</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Accessibility as architecture, not accommodation.</li>
      <li>Experience belongs to the person living it; the witness matters more than the object.</li>
      <li>Technology can increase agency without replacing the human rituals people choose.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
